<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Mu bang ka ngai, kumsawt gam nuom,
 Leh Suongmantam khawpi hawih tak sip zum chu
 Nisa sangin a vak zawi a tiu
 Muh ka nuom ngei Lalpa saulun
 Van mite lenna.

[V2]
 2. Van In nuom zawtna tuonglam chu,
 A sika kensie ziekin bei man ka lau,
 Gitloh nan puon bang ei tuom ziekin,
 Silhpuon bang chan ding ka lau ngei
 Van gam tuol nuom chu.

[V3]
 3. Lalpa, Na lautha puih loh in,
 Sietlei mi na van gam nuom tung theilo ding
 Lau tha al bang manna gam ahi
 Nang hun gingte chungah Lalpa;
 Suolin thimthu lel.

[V4]
 4. Galzo te Zuomang gam nuomah
 Sunni sanga vakzawn laituol leng un au,
 Nuoi simlei lungzinna leh buoina
 Nunnawp nan pak thing bang lun ding
 Lo bang chullo ding.

[V5]
 5. Len ka nuom van gam tuol nuomah.
 Kumsawta I chawlhna ding chu a hawih ngei;
 Lalpa siem Salem Vangkhuo nuomah,
 Laituol nga bangin leng leu hing;
 Ninnawp kim tana.</lyrics>
<title>Suongmantam Khawpi</title>
<hymn_number>237</hymn_number>
<author>V.T. Kappu</author>
</song>